data.description: SELL! SELL! SELL! Make this your Forever Home in Desirable Location! Great character throughout this home located on Nookside Lane that today's Buyer would love to make their own. Nice size living room with a deco fireplace. Adjacent dining room leads to the den with full wall windows. Let your imagination wander in creating your own touch with this roomy eat in kitchen. A half bath in hallway. There is an extra room on this floor that connects to 2 bedrooms with a Jack and Jill full bath. There's a 14 x 21 room above garage with a 3/4 bath and walk in closet that would be great for a home office or Bedroom that is currently not heated. The 2nd floor offers 2 spacious bedrooms and a full bath. Spare room, laundry and half bath in the basement. Enter the garage from the basement. A 2 car attached garage and a 2 car carport. Partially fenced yard. Property is being sold in "AS IS" condition. Cash or Conventional loan only.
